Class PowerUp

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
BurstFirePowerUp, MissilePowerUp, SpaceshipSpeedPowerUp
public abstract class PowerUp
extends MovingObject
Author:
Pierce Forte, Jeff Kim Abstract class that is used for BurstFire, Missile, and Speed powerups. Has common methods like setting activation status
